mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:40:30.000Z","msg":"反正中國又唔守規則<br />\n經濟又就爆<br />\n而家畀人郁手都好正常啦"},{"pid":"c664100334ccd8bd60ce39b6ebb424e2f595ba72","tid":579532,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"自古以嚟都係咁"},{"pid":"1e569acc5c145de769e7cc38b9b22a9389ad866b","tid":579532,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:54:39.000Z","msg":"死鬼佬咁多嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9062ce2b606d52f3cfdecbf040cec4e9b9f2a8","tid":579532,"uid":53172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:56:11.000Z","msg":"趕返中國la"}]}